new class WhileLoopReverse
main method
int count = 5;
count = 5
count = 4
count = 3
count = 2
count = 1
count = 0
Finished the count
--------------------
In the loop, we need to update our variable, so that condition becomes false. we can use ++ or --
++ to count forward
-- to count backwards
int count = 5;
while(count >= 0) {
    System.out.println("count = " + count);
    count--;
}
System.out.println("Finished the count");
